Tasks to complete (Assignment):
1. Create logout functionality in the application & add a "Logout" section in the Navbar for the same.
2. Create functionality for Edit button, under the "About us" Page. 
3. Create your own MERN Application, using as many functionalities as possible (Creating, Deleting, updating, adding, password hashing,
salting, cookies, tokens, navigation, single page application etc, using components, APIs etc.)

Some points about using the source code after downloading :
1. Add your own Username, password, database name, PORT number & secret key, in config.env file.
2. If needed, delete the node modules and reinstall them through terminal. 

NOTE :-
Refer the document called "MERN Application Notes" in the main folder, to get the notes consisting of the flow of the entire application.
